EN: Brightness will bring hope.

ZH: 我期待着未来的光明。
EN: I look forward to the brightness of the future.

ZH: 光明正照耀在我们身上。
EN: Brightness is shining upon us.

ZH: 光明将战胜黑暗。
EN: Light will overcome darkness.

