EN: The clouds dispersing, light appears.

ZH: 天边透着一缕光明。
EN: A ray of light shining through the sky.

ZH: 光明将引导我们走向成功。
EN: Brightness will guide us towards success.

ZH: 我们要相信光明总会到来。
EN: We must believe that brightness will always come.

ZH: 他那拥有一双温暖光明的眼睛。
EN: He has warm bright eyes. 

ZH: 光明之路长，但却不可缺席。
EN: The road to brightness is long, but one must not absent.
